Class ProcessorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.illinois.ncsa.daffodil.japi.WithDiagnostics
      • edu.illinois.ncsa.daffodil.japi.ProcessorFactory

  • public class ProcessorFactory
extends WithDiagnostics
    Factory to create DataProcessor's, used for parsing data

    Do not use the ProcessorFactry constructor to create a ProcessorFactory. Instead, use Compiler.compileFile(java.io.File)

        public void setDistinguishedRootNode(java.lang.String name,

        Parameters:

        DataProcessor used to parse data. Must check WithDiagnostics.isError() before using it.
